International Journal of Robotic Engineering



ISSN : 2631-5106; Impact Factor = 1.10; DOI: 10.35840/2631-5106



Dear Dr. Foaad Khosmood,



Hope you are doing well!



We are writing to enquire about your availability of writing an article for
<https://www.vibgyorpublishers.org/journals/International-Journal-of-Robotic
-Engineering.php> International Journal of Robotic Engineering from any
discipline for its upcoming issue. It is an open-access, peer-reviewed
academic journal promotes the various interdisciplinary aspects of Robotics
and Bot Engineering.



I wonder if you could submit manuscript (Original Article, Reviews, Mini
Reviews, Commentaries, etc.) for the International Journal of Robotic
Engineering. We would appreciate receiving your submission on or before
January 15, 2020.



Kindly submit your valuable work at:
<https://www.vibgyorpublishers.org/login.php>
https://www.vibgyorpublishers.org/login.php or send it as an e-mail
attachment to this mail.



Please do not hesitate to ask for any further queries.



We are awaiting your positive response.



With thanks,



Francesco Carraro (Managing Editor)

Editorial office | International Journal of Robotic Engineering (ISSN
2631-5106)

VIBGYOR ePress

313 Kd Tower, Cotterells

Hemel Hempstead, Hertfordshire

England, HP1 1AU





Note: Reply as unsubscribe if you don't want to receive any further mails
from us.

